body:
So me and my friend are starting a team and i'm trying to pick my role, he wants ADC so i'm not going to complain i really don't enjoy ADC enough. I've been playing a lot of mid lately i love it, just being able to have the chance for the 1v1 kills and playing Zed and destroying someone in lane feels great. But i also thought about Jungle and Support, I like roaming and providing vision for my team. One reason i don't really want to play support is because I want to have that chance to make crazy plays (Kill wise, Yes i know supports can make crazy plays too). I thought about jungle too, I love jungle, being able to roam/gank the whole game and deny/provide vision is great. Top lane just is not my thing I don't like being a huge tank i want to be able to make crazy plays. So it really comes down to Mid or Jungle.

Anything to help me decide?

